channel.title: TF2 Soundtrack - Right Behind You (Eswyn EDM Cover)
channel.description:
So one thing I like to do for practice is listen to a song and transcribe the notes. I do this typically for EDM, say for the chord progression. I decided to try it out on some TF2 soundtracks, because I really like them. This one I started to get carried away with, and added a little twist to the end. I just felt like sharing it with you all. I hope you like it!
Mine: https://soundcloud.com/eswyn/tf2-soundtrack-right-behind/s-wjOP9 Original: https://youtu.be/ciL7OKWSu10
